{"color":"DEFAULT","isTrashed":false,"isPinned":false,"isArchived":false,"textContent":"Lat pulldown - 40 kg 10, 45 kg 10, 50 kg > 45 kg 8 NROM > NROM, 40 kg 5 slow... 5 fast... 1 hold 5 sec\nRear delt fly - 77 lbs 10, 77 lbs > 66 lbs 7>3, 10>3\nChest-supported rows - 2x(15 kg + 5 kg) 8, 10, 2x(15kg + 10 kg) 6...3 NROM\nDb shrugs / Lat raise - 30 lbs / 20 lbs 15>10, 30 lbs / 15 lbs 15/10, 15/10\nArnold machine - 2x5 kg each 10, 10, 2x5kg+2.5kg each 10\nBack machine - 20 kg each 8~8, 8*~8**, 6**~6**\nPreacher curl - bar + 2x5 kg 10, bar + 2x(5kg+2.5kg) 8, 2x(5kg+2.5kg) > 2x5kg 6>2...1F\nBarbell rows - 2x15 kg 10, 2x(15 kg + 5 kg) 10, 8, 2x(15kg + 5kg + 2.5kg) > 2x(15kg+ 5kg) 4>4\nFace pull - 35 kg 10, 40 kg 10, 45 kg > 40 kg 7F>3F\nForearm curl / Reverse forearm curl - 15 lbs / 10 lbs 15/10, 15/10, 15/10\nBicep curls - 20 lbs > 15 lbs 5~6...2~2>4~4, 4~4...1~1>2~2...2~2, 5~3...1~1>2~2...2~2\n\nNotes:\n* - NROM on last rep\n** - NROM from 2nd to the last rep\n\nWeight - ","title":"February 5, 2026","userEditedTimestampUsec":1770300797315000,"createdTimestampUsec":1770288545722000,"textContentHtml":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Lat pulldown - 40 kg 10, 45 kg 10, 50 kg &gt; 45 kg 8 NROM &gt; NROM, 40 kg 5 slow... 5 fast... 1 hold 5 sec<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Rear delt fly - 77 lbs 10, 77 lbs &gt; 66 lbs 7&gt;3, 10&gt;3<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt